Name: HaselTweaks
Changelog:
New "Tweak": Commands

A variety of useful chat commands.

Starting with:

- `/itemlink <id>`  
  Prints an item link for the given item id in chat.
- `/whatmount`  
  Target a player and execute the command to see what mount your target is riding and which item teaches this mount.

 Other changes
- [DTR] Entries are now created on load (instead on setup) and removed on unload (instead on dispose)
- A better tweak tooltip has been added to the tweaks list
- A tweak is now marked as outdated if the signature fails
